      the "blank page" problem (Closes: #215231).
    - Avoid the conversion of "open" in scripts to "PrivoxyWindowOpen"
      (Closes: #197995). 
    - "advocancy" is no longer blocked (Closes: #202042).
    - Fixed yet another two memory leaks (Closes: #215911).
