    upstream package.
  * Create doc/pdf, which is missing upstream.
  * disable filter{unsolicited-popups} for www.perl.com/language/newdocs/pod/ 
    to avoid problems with "PrivoxyWindowOpen" in Perl manuals
    (Closes: #195311).
